result.title: Denial of judgement
result.content:
My solution of Problem D of Div2 contest of round 236(http://codeforces.com/contest/402/problem/D) is receiving Denial of judgement error. Could anyone please explain to me what is the problem?

The Submissions Ids are

http://codeforces.com/contest/402/submission/16409847 http://codeforces.com/contest/402/submission/16409976 http://codeforces.com/contest/402/submission/16420324

Someone please tell me what should be the countermeasure. Thanks in advance.

Update: I think codeforces has fixed the issue. There isn't Denial of judgement error anymore.

Thanks everyone for commenting. :)
